@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_ohplip(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = wp.abs(v2)
    v0 = (0.66 * (v2 - wp.cos(v0 + 0.15)))
    v0 = tmp
    v1 = ((wp.sin(v0 + 0.05) / 0.78) * ((tmp + 0.70 - v1 + 0.92) + wp.sin(tmp + 0.09)))
    v2 = 0.82
    tmp = v0
    data[tid] = v0
